page.title: 11Door-to-door Survey 2
page.content: ROSE COTTAGE The house was built 120 years ago,and is constructed of brick and flint.The roof is made from slate.The majority of food for the cottage comes from the nearby butchers.The land around the house is mostly owned by Goodwood Estate.The occupants came from Duncton,in 1982. THE FOX AND HOUNDS PUBLIC HOUSE This building has been a pub ever since it was built,300 years ago.It is popular with the villagers,who prefer it to the Horse and Groom(Singleton's other pub.) THE MODERN HOUSING ESTATE The small estate was built in 1984,and is sited in the grounds of the manor house .The house owners found the area quiet and the locals friendly.The houses are sited near the Fox and Hounds and the Post Office.
